More Positives Good nights sleep free internet access with a printer for the residents gym on 10th floor with the added bonus of an open air leisure area beside it.	The hotel provides great breakfast (cooked and continental), a great gym and a superb roof terrace.	The room cannot be faulted, with a spacious terrace, super comfy bed and the best hotel bathroom (two rain-showers and bath) and stylish decor.	The hotel was stylish and very clean, with helpful staff, a business center with free internet access and a printer.